captainSkill.description: Increases ally ATK by 25% in Infected faction content.

voiceLines.summon: Scorpion blood runs where law has failed.
Relax, darling. I only stab people who pay late.
voiceLines.death: Guess the house wins… this time…

voiceLines.summon: You found me. Must really be desperate.
voiceLines.death: Tell… Lila Hart… keep the fire burning…

voiceLines.summon: Field medic, ex-corporate. Let’s patch this world up.
voiceLines.lowHp: Not the first time I’ve bled for a cause.
voiceLines.ultimate: No one dies on my watch!

voiceLines.summon: You’ve stepped into the sanctuary. Now, breathe.
voiceLines.lowHp: Pain is only another form of insight.
voiceLines.ultimate: See what the virus has shown me.

voiceLines.summon: KingsTech taught me everything. Now I’ll burn their lesson plans.
voiceLines.lowHp: Heh. They hit harder in the labs.
voiceLines.death: If I fall… someone else will leak the truth…

voiceLines.summon: The pack moves where I lead.
Bioengineering major, reporting for extremely unsafe duty.
voiceLines.lowHp: Note to self… reinforce this prototype.
voiceLines.ultimate: Let’s see what this baby can do!

voiceLines.summon: If I can map the virus, I can map this war.
voiceLines.lowHp: Too much input… but I’m not done.
voiceLines.ultimate: Let me show you true sensory overflow.

voiceLines.summon: Alright, team—deep breath. We’re gonna sweat through this.
voiceLines.lowHp: I’ve had worse from leg day!

voiceLines.summon: Welcome to Leo’s—today’s special is chaos.
voiceLines.lowHp: Okay wow, that’s above my pay grade.

voiceLines.summon: I… I’ll try my best. Please don’t leave me.
voiceLines.lowHp: No— I can’t go back there!

voiceLines.summon: You pay, I smash. Easy deal.
voiceLines.lowHp: Okay, okay, maybe I picked the wrong mark.

voiceLines.summon: Orders received. Area will be secured.
Stay calm, I’ve got enough stims for everyone.
voiceLines.ultimate: No one dies on my watch.

voiceLines.summon: Dropped out of class, enrolled in chaos.
voiceLines.lowHp: Yeah, this is worse than exams.

voiceLines.summon: I know every shortcut in these tunnels.
voiceLines.lowHp: Guess I ran into the wrong corner.
